No space between function name and first open parenthesis except in function definition.

OK...

function somefunc (params) {}
var = func(params);

NOT OK...

function somefunc(params) {}
var = func (params)



1 space between first open parenthesis and paramater if parameter is a function.

OK...

func(var)
func( func2(var) )
func( func2( func3(var) ) )

NOT OK...
func(func2(var))


1 space between first open and last closed parenthesis in all conditionals.

OK..

if ( $var ) 
if ( func($var) ) 
